            <title>Write for Internet</title>
            <link>http://localhost:53376/page/write-for-us/</link>
            <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:53376/page/write-for-us/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;We welcome contributions from the community! Whether it&amp;rsquo;s a technical tutorial, a deep dive into Swift/Go features, or a career advice piece, we&amp;rsquo;d love to host it.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-developer-way-github-workflow&#34;&gt;The Developer Way (GitHub Workflow)&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since this blog is open source, contributing is as simple as submitting a Pull Request (PR).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-fork--clone&#34;&gt;1. Fork &amp;amp; Clone&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Go to &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/ckdash-git/blogs&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;our GitHub repo&lt;/a&gt; and click the &lt;strong&gt;Fork&lt;/strong&gt; button in the top-right corner.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Clone your fork locally:&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;git clone https://github.com/&amp;lt;YOUR-USERNAME&amp;gt;/blogs.git&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; blogs&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Create a new branch for your post:&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;git checkout -b post/my-new-article&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-create-your-post&#34;&gt;2. Create Your Post&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We use &lt;strong&gt;Page Bundles&lt;/strong&gt; to keep images and content organized.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Create a new folder in &lt;code&gt;content/blogs/&lt;/code&gt; with your slug (URL friendly name):&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;mkdir content/blogs/my-awesome-post&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Create an &lt;code&gt;index.md&lt;/code&gt; file inside that folder.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Copy and paste the following &lt;strong&gt;Front Matter&lt;/strong&gt; at the top of your &lt;code&gt;index.md&lt;/code&gt; file:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;---&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;title: &amp;#34;My Awesome Post Title&amp;#34;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;date: 2026-02-07&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;description: &amp;#34;A short, catchy summary of your article.&amp;#34;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;image: &amp;#34;hero-image.png&amp;#34; # Optional: Place image in the same folder&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;authors: [&amp;#34;your-github-username&amp;#34;]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;tags: [&amp;#34;Swift&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;Tutorial&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;Beginner&amp;#34;]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;---&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt; 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Start writing your content here...&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-writing-content&#34;&gt;3. Writing Content&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Images&lt;/strong&gt;: Place image files directly in your post folder (e.g., &lt;code&gt;content/blogs/my-awesome-post/screenshot.png&lt;/code&gt;) and reference them simply by filename: &lt;code&gt;![Alt Text](screenshot.png)&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code Blocks&lt;/strong&gt;: Use triple backticks with the language name for syntax highlighting:&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-swift&#34; data-lang=&#34;swift&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#50fa7b&#34;&gt;hello&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;